name: nerd xx
description:
for females

60 ml / 2 fl. oz.

If it smells like perfume, that's because it is. 

A clean, refreshing, uplifting scent with notes of jasmine and carnations

If it smells as though you are being airbrushed into a somber and monochromatic existence... if it smells like a celebrity was overpaid to read to you from an inane, over-written script... if it smells like an unlikely romantic adventure that necessitates wind-swept hair and narration by a raspy-voiced European... we'll have to revisit our formula.

ingredients: alc. denat., fragrance, water.

DUE TO THE NATURE OF THE PRODUCT, WE ARE UNABLE TO ACCEPT RETURNS.  ALL SALES ARE FINAL.

name: nerd xy
description:
for males

60 ml / 2 fl. oz 

If it smells like cologne, that's because it is. 

A subtle yet rich woodsy scent with floral notes and a touch a mint.

If it smells like throngs of beautiful, pouting models caressing your washboard abs while finding shelter from the rain in some vague but exotic locale... if it smells like triumph in a pick-up game among questionably picturesque comrades... if it smells like sexual escapades in conspicuously poor lighting conditions with an ominous, nondescript hard rock musical track... we'll have to revisit our formula.

ingredients: alc. denat., fragrance, water.

DUE TO THE NATURE OF THE PRODUCT, WE ARE UNABLE TO ACCEPT RETURNS.  ALL SALES ARE FINAL.
